Philip Abbott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_Abbott 0 Philip Abbott (March 20, 1924 – February 23, 1998) was an American character actor. He appeared in several films and numerous television series, including a lead role as Arthur Ward in the crime series The F.B.I.. Abbott was also the founder of Theatre West in Los Angeles.
